import{_ as t,o,c as a,a2 as r}from"./chunks/framework.C766EroN.js";const d=JSON.parse('{"title":"Customization 定制","description":"NetBox 定制功能","frontmatter":{"title":"Customization 定制","description":"NetBox 定制功能"},"headers":[],"relativePath":"tech-share/netbox/4.5.1/community/features/customization.md","filePath":"tech-share/netbox/4.5.1/community/features/customization.md"}'),s={name:"tech-share/netbox/4.5.1/community/features/customization.md"};function i(n,e,c,l,p,u){return o(),a("div",null,[...e[0]||(e[0]=[r('<h1 id="customization-定制" tabindex="-1">Customization / 定制 <a class="header-anchor" href="#customization-定制" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Customization / 定制&quot;">​</a></h1><p><em>内容来源 / Source: <a href="https://netboxlabs.com/docs/netbox/features/customization/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">NetBox Labs Documentation</a> | 如有侵权请<a href="/contact.html">联系我们</a>删除</em></p><p>While NetBox strives to meet the needs of every network, the needs of users to cater to their own unique environments cannot be ignored. NetBox was built with this in mind, and can be customized in many ways to better suit your particular needs.</p><p>虽然 NetBox 努力满足每个网络的需求，但用户满足其独特环境的需求不容忽视。NetBox 就是考虑到这一点而构建的，可以通过多种方式进行定制以更好地满足您的特定需求。</p><p>For end‑user personalization topics (bookmarks, table preferences, language, CSV delimiter, and more), see <a href="https://netboxlabs.com/docs/netbox/features/user-preferences/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Features &gt; User Preferences</a>.</p><p>对于最终用户个性化主题（书签、表首选项、语言、CSV 分隔符等），请参阅 <a href="https://netboxlabs.com/docs/netbox/features/user-preferences/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Features &gt; User Preferences</a>。</p><p>Most objects in NetBox can be assigned user-created tags to aid with organization and filtering. Tag values are completely arbitrary: They may be used to store data in key-value pairs, or they may be employed simply as labels against which objects can be filtered.</p><p>NetBox 中的大多数对象可以分配用户创建的标签以帮助组织和过滤。标签值完全是任意的：它们可以用于以键值对存储数据，或者可以简单地用作可以过滤对象的标签。</p><h2 id="custom-fields-自定义字段" tabindex="-1">Custom Fields / 自定义字段 <a class="header-anchor" href="#custom-fields-自定义字段" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Custom Fields / 自定义字段&quot;">​</a></h2><p>While NetBox provides a rather extensive data model out of the box, the need may arise to store certain additional data associated with NetBox objects. NetBox administrators can create custom fields on built-in objects to meet these needs.</p><p>虽然 NetBox 开箱即用提供了相当广泛的数据模型，但可能需要存储与 NetBox 对象关联的某些额外数据。NetBox 管理员可以在内置对象上创建自定义字段以满足这些需求。</p><p>NetBox supports many types of custom field, from basic data types like strings and integers, to complex structures like selection lists or raw JSON. It&#39;s even possible to add a custom field which references other NetBox objects.</p><p>NetBox 支持多种类型的自定义字段，从字符串和整数等基本数据类型到选择列表或原始 JSON 等复杂结构。甚至可以添加引用其他 NetBox 对象的自定义字段。</p><h2 id="custom-links-自定义链接" tabindex="-1">Custom Links / 自定义链接 <a class="header-anchor" href="#custom-links-自定义链接" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Custom Links / 自定义链接&quot;">​</a></h2><p>Custom links allow you to conveniently reference external resources related to NetBox objects from within the NetBox UI. For example, you might wish to link each virtual machine modeled in NetBox to its corresponding view in some orchestration application.</p><p>自定义链接允许您从 NetBox UI 内方便地引用与 NetBox 对象相关的外部资源。例如，您可能希望将 NetBox 中建模的每台虚拟机链接到某些编排应用程序中的相应视图。</p><h2 id="custom-validation-自定义验证" tabindex="-1">Custom Validation / 自定义验证 <a class="header-anchor" href="#custom-validation-自定义验证" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Custom Validation / 自定义验证&quot;">​</a></h2><p>While NetBox employs robust built-in object validation to ensure the integrity of its database, you might wish to enforce additional rules governing the creation and modification of certain objects. You can configure a custom validation rule in NetBox to enforce these requirements.</p><p>虽然 NetBox 采用强大的内置对象验证来确保其数据库的完整性，但您可能希望强制执行管理某些对象的创建和修改的额外规则。您可以在 NetBox 中配置自定义验证规则以强制执行这些要求。</p><h2 id="export-templates-导出模板" tabindex="-1">Export Templates / 导出模板 <a class="header-anchor" href="#export-templates-导出模板" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Export Templates / 导出模板&quot;">​</a></h2><p>Most NetBox objects can be exported in bulk in two built-in CSV formats. NetBox also provides the capability to define your own custom data export formats via export templates. An export template is essentially <a href="https://jinja.palletsprojects.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Jinja2</a> template code associated with a particular object type.</p><p>大多数 NetBox 对象可以以两种内置 CSV 格式批量导出。NetBox 还提供通过导出模板定义您自己的自定义数据导出格式的能力。导出模板本质上与特定对象类型关联的 <a href="https://jinja.palletsprojects.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Jinja2</a> 模板代码。</p><h2 id="reports-报告" tabindex="-1">Reports / 报告 <a class="header-anchor" href="#reports-报告" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Reports / 报告&quot;">​</a></h2><p>NetBox administrators can install custom Python scripts, known as reports, which run within NetBox and can be executed and analyzed within the NetBox UI. Reports are a great way to evaluate NetBox objects against a set of arbitrary rules.</p><p>NetBox 管理员可以安装称为报告的自定义 Python 脚本，这些脚本在 NetBox 内运行，可以在 NetBox UI 中执行和分析。报告是根据一组任意规则评估 NetBox 对象的好方法。</p><h2 id="custom-scripts-自定义脚本" tabindex="-1">Custom Scripts / 自定义脚本 <a class="header-anchor" href="#custom-scripts-自定义脚本" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;Custom Scripts / 自定义脚本&quot;">​</a></h2><p>Custom scripts are similar to reports, but more powerful. A custom script can prompt the user for input via a form (or API data), and is built to do much more than just reporting. Custom scripts are generally used to automate tasks, such as the population of new objects in NetBox, or exchanging data with external systems.</p><p>自定义脚本与报告类似，但更强大。自定义脚本可以通过表单（或 API 数据）提示用户输入，并构建为不仅仅是报告。自定义脚本通常用于自动化任务，例如在 NetBox 中填充新对象或与外部系统交换数据。</p>',28)])])}const h=t(s,[["render",i]]);export{d as __pageData,h as default};
